contentrichtext.text: '''NGE''' can mean: * [[Neon Genesis Evangelion]], a number of works in anime/manga franchise of the same name * [[Nagoya Grampus Eight]], a soccer club playing for J-League * [[New Georgia Encyclopedia]], a web-based encyclopedia about the US state of Georgia * [[The Nation of Gods and Earths]] or '''5 % Nation''', a non religious movement that views Islam as a culture and a way of life * New Game Enhancements, a set of changes to the computer game ''[[Star Wars Galaxies]]'' * NGE, an abbreviation for the [[Ngage]] portable game console by Nokia * [[National Greek Examination]], an examination for the [[ancient Greek language]] {{disambig}}
